# Copy to `.dev.vars` and fill in. Wrangler loads this file for `wrangler dev`.

# Required — signing secret for Better Auth sessions.
# Generate with: openssl rand -base64 32
BETTER_AUTH_SECRET=replace-me-with-32-plus-char-random-secret

# Optional — enable "Continue with GitHub" on the login page. Set both to
# the values from your GitHub OAuth app (callback URL:
# http://localhost:5173/api/auth/callback/github).
# GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=
# GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=
